{"tid":1564901,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[915主線] 願榮光歸香港上咗紐約時報！受訪者：中國國歌對我冇意義，唱榮光令我好有歸屬感！","createTime":"2019-09-13T02:52:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T01:40:35.000Z","uid":36592,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9022c9ede89ab819d04ae3699f86257cfdc38f50","tid":1564901,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:52:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2019/09/12/world/asia/glory-to-hong-kong-anthem.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2019%2F09%2F12%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fglory-to-hong-kong-anthem.html&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmJKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=a0ebb118\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2019/09/12/world/asia/glory-to-hong-kong-anthem.html</a><br />\n<br />\n（重點節錄）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Hong Kong Protesters, Without an Anthem to Sing, Create One Online</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\nNg Kwok Lun, a 30-year-old videographer, was one of hundreds of people to sing the song on Tuesday at Tuen Mun Town Center, a shopping mall. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">He said he felt &ldquo;a great sense of belonging&rdquo; that he had never felt while listening to China&rsquo;s anthem</span></strong>, &ldquo;March of the Volunteers.&rdquo; (A survey of residents in June by the University of Hong Kong found that 76 percent of respondents identified themselves as Hong Kongers, while just 23 percent identified as Chinese.)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;I don&rsquo;t think the stories inside the lyrics mean anything to me,&rdquo; he said of the Chinese anthem. &ldquo;But when I listen to the song of Hong Kong, I understand every word in the lyrics. It recalls everything we have done for the past few months, how we get here.&rdquo;</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n[DGX團隊]《願榮光歸香港》正式進行曲版 《Glory to Hong Kong》Formal March Edition<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YxptkMBYk2A&amp;ab_channel=dgxdgx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYxptkMBYk2A%26ab_channel%3Ddgxdgx&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmJKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=29b96cf0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YxptkMBYk2A&amp;ab_channel=dgxdgx</a>"},{"pid":"84aa85aad3f6376a6aea705def578821225b13ec","tid":1564901,"uid":25185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:52:13.000Z","msg":"【 突發】和理塞 商場篇 終於出爐!922第一彈約定你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1563867\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1563867</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTG :<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEgVehN8bY_NbBDM8g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAEgVehN8bY_NbBDM8g&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmJKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=8b2a91d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEgVehN8bY_NbBDM8g</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Whua26P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWhua26P.jpg&h=0a307b31&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g0SzLka.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg0SzLka.jpg&h=aa4ea6e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee8832373e64d9ecbeaf44821d29c227eca5b2e8","tid":1564901,"uid":36592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:52:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請關注新屋嶺集中營<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n新屋嶺全部義士已認罪 ！用幾十個手足條命換呢個核彈返黎！！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1558432\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1558432</a><br />\n<br />\n終極戰線：酷刑！想美國同全世界做野，就全力追究新屋嶺酷刑同831太子酷刑！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1557408\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1557408</a><br />\n<br />\n全世界集中火力係新屋嶺上面唔該<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1556103\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1556103</a><br />\n<br />\n[正式宣布] 新屋嶺事件為香港抗爭史上最黑暗事件<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1554685\" data-aut